{"article_id":"ZIzJxdIUgWKTOe5B","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Romney Tempers Foreign Policy Criticism After Flap Over Libya Remarks","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Appearing in Virginia on Thursday ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Republican Mitt Romney tried to bring his campaign back to the issues","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"he has focused on before in the swing state :","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"the nation 's economy and strengthening the military .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"A day after Romney ignited a debate over his criticism of President Obama 's handling of events in Libya and Egypt ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"the Republican presidential nominee largely steered clear of discussing unrest in Egypt and the attack on an American consulate in Benghazi , Libya ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that left four Americans dead .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"The violence ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"sparked by an anti-Islam film ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"on Thursday spread into Yemen ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"where protesters stormed the U.S. Embassy compound .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"At a rally in Fairfax , Va. , Romney began his speech","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"by telling the crowd ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"`` we 're in mourning '' for Ambassador Chris Stevens and the three other embassy staffers","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"killed .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"`` We 've lost four of our diplomats across the world .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"We 're thinking about their families and those","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"that they 've left behind .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"What a tragedy","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"to lose such wonderful people","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"that have been so wonderful","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"and [ we ] appreciate their service to the country . ''","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"Romney largely stayed away from the controversy","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"surrounding his claims on Tuesday","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"that the Obama administration","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"- through its embassy in Egypt -","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"made statements `` akin to an apology . ''","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"Romney had faced strong backlash ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"including some from fellow Republicans ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"for his aggressive response to an unfolding international incident .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"During Romney 's Thursday speech , a heckler yelled ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"`` Why are you politicizing Libya ? ''","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"NPR 's Ari Shapiro , on the trail with the Romney campaign , said","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"the crowd attempted to drown out the heckler","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"by chanting ,","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"`` Mitt '' and `` U-S-A ! ''","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"Romney responded","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"saying :","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"`` I would offer a moment of silence ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"but one gentleman does n't want to be silent ,","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"so we 're going to keep on going . ''","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"President Obama traveled to Golden , Colo. , Thursday ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"where he spoke about improving the economy","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"- but not before he vowed to find those","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"who killed Stevens .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"`` I want people around the world to hear me :","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"To all those","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"who would do us harm ,","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"no act of terror will go unpunished .","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"It will not dim the light of the values","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"that we proudly present to the rest of the world .","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"No act of violence shakes the resolve of the United States of America , ''","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"Obama said .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"On Thursday , Libyan officials informed the U.S.","depth":4},{"id":55,"text":"that four people were in custody in connection with the attack .","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"During his speech in Virginia , Romney reiterated a general vision of a United States","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"`` that 's strong ,","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"that helps lead the world . ...","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"As we watch the world today","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"sometimes it seems that we 're at the mercy of events","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"instead of shaping events ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"and a strong America 's essential to shape events . ''","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":125,"left":0,"right":124,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":117,"right":123,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":117,"left":115,"right":116,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":115,"left":66,"right":114,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":66,"left":1,"right":65,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":65,"left":64,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":72,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":68,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":5,"right":67,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":67,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":70,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":69,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":69,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":82,"right":112,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":82,"left":12,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":74,"right":80,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":13,"right":73,"relatio